    <h1>Semrush Review 2026: The $140/Month Question Nobody Answers Honestly</h1>
    <p class="description">Semrush is the most comprehensive SEO platform on the market — over 26 billion keywords, 142 countries, 55+ tools in one tab. It is also <strong>$139–$499/mo for data, not content</strong>. After 30 days inside Pro, Guru, and Business — plus interviews with 16 paying customers — here is the honest 2026 verdict and the real monthly cost most reviews skip.</p>
